name: Jennifer Salazar
text:
This place is one of the best Pizza Hut I've ever been in.
The food was made with love it has a good amount of toppings on every slide, the crust was nice and crunchy on the bottom but the top was noce and fluffy.
Great people helping you out. I walked in and out with my pick up order. Thank you!

name: Lorenzo de Pacas
text: Friday night 8:30 this place is busy, short-staffed, no manager in sight, out if 3 of their 4 pizza crusts, turned in online order for two pastas and a large pizza, got home one pasta is wrong, had to bring it back as no one answered my â€¦More

name: Sailor Permenter
text: Friendly staff even if you come in right before closing. Their food improved a lot since my last visit and was fresh and full of flavor. Definitely might come here more often now. Thank you for the meal!

name: erin Crawford
text: The breadsticks and wings were some of the best I have ever had. They were cooked perfectly. The manager was friendly and attentive. This was literally the best service I have ever had at a Pizza Hut.

name: m shell
text: Extremely nice manager! They pizza and wings where cooked perfect and were delicious! I will definitely be eating there again!

name: Tammy Hollandsworth
text: Best time to gather together with your church family!  The food and company a long with the best service in Anthony Kansas!

name: Tamara Pifer
text: Pizza was great and our waiter Austin was working the floor himself and was working his butt off.Did a great job.

name: B.Yvette Cordova-Cambron
text: Very nice people, clean and quick service.

name: corey arvie
text: The cook made and insult about my size on the way to be seated. Not good and very disrespectful.

name: Amabelly Barrera
text: Staff is always so helpful, always welcomes you with a great sense of humor, food always hot!! Best Pizza Hut ever!!

name: Lucinda Gates
text: Friendly caring staff! Online orders are ready in great time!

name: CARMEN ATHERTON
text: DEPENDS ON WHAT TIME YOU GO IN...SOME EMPLOYEES ARE GREAT AND A COUPLE THAT SEEM LIKE THEY REALLY DON'T WANT TO BE BOTHERED...PIZZA CRUST SOMETIMES TASTE REAL STALE...LIKE THE DOUGH HAS BEEN SITTING AROUND FOR AWHILE...

name: Alin Pass
text: What can I say? It's good

name: Brandi Drouhard
text: Food was good hot and server was very good

name: chris caldwell
text: Food is great but the service leave something to be desired

name: Carol Lucas
text: Food was good& so was the service.

name: Aaron Patterson
text: Staff is always friendly and helpful.

name: Summer Burton
text: Always friendly and always scrumptious!! Thank you!!

name: Miranda Shore
text: Friendly people. Buffet. Pizza is okay
